title: Dialogos as Healer with Peter Czaplinsky -Voices with Vervaeke
description:
Peter Czaplinsky is a psychiatrist who reached out to me because he wanted to discuss and mystical experience that occurred within a therapeutic session. I was deeply intrigued by this intersection of the dialogical, the mystical, and the therapeutic.  This dialogos with Peter surpassed my expectations. It is truly beautiful.

Peter's website:  http://doctorpeter.ca/
